msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Democracy x AI Cohort | Mozilla Foundation"
msgstr "Democracy x AI Cohort | Fundación Mozilla"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "The Democracy x AI cohort is founded on the hypothesis that, if built differently, AI could strengthen democracy rather than erode it."
msgstr "La cohorte Democracy x AI se basa en la hipótesis de que, si se construyera de manera diferente, la IA podría fortalecer la democracia en lugar de erosionarla."

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Democracy x AI Cohort"
msgstr "Democracy x AI Cohort"

msgctxt "hero_title"
msgid "Democracy x AI Cohort"
msgstr "Democracy x AI Cohort"

msgctxt "hero_description"
msgid "A better, more democratic tech future isn’t just possible. It’s still ours to build."
msgstr "Un futuro tecnológico mejor y más democrático no solo es posible; todavía está en nuestras manos construirlo."

msgctxt "hero_image_alt_text"
msgid "Yellow shape with cut out of sky and squiggle"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.0db225b9-f286-40f1-8294-7f9ae7075745.title"
msgid "Imagine AI that’s built so more people have a say in what’s next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.a7c88a8e-4a1f-433d-9ad9-2e4ef238e966.left_column.60e4b64a-28a8-4fcd-be7f-b6b031ca4764"
msgid ""
"We’ve been sold the idea that a better future is more efficient, moves faster, and is one where human judgment can be engineered away. The logic is all around us. It’s in the technology we use, the "
"devices we wear, and the systems that shape our lives."
msgstr ""
"Nos han vendido la idea de que un futuro mejor es más eficiente, avanza más rápido y es aquel en el que el juicio humano puede eliminarse mediante la ingeniería. Esta lógica nos rodea por todas "
"partes. Está en la tecnología que usamos, en los dispositivos que llevamos y en los sistemas que dan forma a nuestras vidas."

msgctxt "body.a7c88a8e-4a1f-433d-9ad9-2e4ef238e966.left_column.60e4b64a-28a8-4fcd-be7f-b6b031ca4764"
msgid "But"
msgstr "Pero"

msgctxt "body.a7c88a8e-4a1f-433d-9ad9-2e4ef238e966.left_column.60e4b64a-28a8-4fcd-be7f-b6b031ca4764"
msgid "Democracy isn’t meant to be optimized."
msgstr "la democracia no está pensada para optimizarse."

msgctxt "body.a7c88a8e-4a1f-433d-9ad9-2e4ef238e966.left_column.60e4b64a-28a8-4fcd-be7f-b6b031ca4764"
msgid "The messiness and friction are the point. Disagreement and compromise aren’t obstacles that need fixing. They’re essential to how democracy works."
msgstr "El desorden y la fricción son precisamente la cuestión. El desacuerdo y el compromiso no son obstáculos que haya que resolver; son elementos esenciales del funcionamiento de la democracia."

msgctxt "body.a7c88a8e-4a1f-433d-9ad9-2e4ef238e966.left_column.60e4b64a-28a8-4fcd-be7f-b6b031ca4764"
msgid ""
"The Democracy x AI cohort is founded on the hypothesis that, if built differently, AI could strengthen democracy rather than erode it. Global by design, this cohort reflects the understanding that "
"technology doesn’t emerge from a vacuum: its politics shape its possibilities. We curate the cohort so ideas move across borders, as they should."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.a7c88a8e-4a1f-433d-9ad9-2e4ef238e966.left_column.60e4b64a-28a8-4fcd-be7f-b6b031ca4764"
msgid "These ten projects are turning imagination into infrastructure, creating new tools and systems that keep human judgment at the center of democratic life."
msgstr "Estos diez proyectos están convirtiendo la imaginación en infraestructura al crear nuevas herramientas y sistemas que mantienen el juicio humano en el centro de la vida democrática."

msgctxt "body.a1500344-1ed4-4703-ab5e-3e6414719d40.title"
msgid "Explore What They’re Building"
msgstr "Explora lo que están construyendo"

msgctxt "body.774237fc-2826-42ca-9c45-658e9e27e4f4.left_column.10d7b183-5ebe-4437-b3c4-21997061a1c4"
msgid ""
"While these projects are grounded in distinct democratic contexts around the world, they are united by a shared hypothesis: that, if built differently, AI can strengthen democracy while preserving "
"the human judgment it depends on."
msgstr ""
"Aunque estos proyectos están arraigados en contextos democráticos distintos en todo el mundo, los une una hipótesis compartida: si se construye de manera diferente, la IA puede fortalecer la "
"democracia y preservar al mismo tiempo el juicio humano del que depende."

msgctxt "body.774237fc-2826-42ca-9c45-658e9e27e4f4.left_column.10d7b183-5ebe-4437-b3c4-21997061a1c4"
msgid ""
"Over the next 12 months, these ten project teams will advance their work through our Incubator, receiving coaching, expert advice, and peer mentorship as they build and test new ways to strengthen "
"democracy in the age of AI."
msgstr ""
"Durante los próximos 12 meses, estos diez equipos de proyecto avanzarán en su trabajo a través de nuestra Incubadora, recibiendo orientación, asesoramiento experto y mentoría entre pares mientras "
"desarrollan y prueban nuevas formas de fortalecer la democracia en la era de la IA."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.24355ed7-0c4b-4136-b95e-41815b4dcec9.title"
msgid "Baisoku Kaigi"
msgstr "Baisoku Kaigi"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.24355ed7-0c4b-4136-b95e-41815b4dcec9.description"
msgid ""
"<i>From Plural Reality (Japan):</i> Inspired by democratic challenges in Otoineppu, a Japanese village facing population decline, <a id=\"a1\">this tool helps residents understand and express their "
"views</a> before participating in community deliberation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.24355ed7-0c4b-4136-b95e-41815b4dcec9.description"
msgid "Uses an adaptive LLM questioning loop to clarify individual positions, then maps them with PCA-based opinion clustering to identify consensus, factual disputes, and value differences."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza un ciclo adaptativo de preguntas de LLM para clarificar las posiciones individuales y, a continuación, las mapea mediante agrupación de opiniones basada en PCA para identificar consensos, "
"desacuerdos sobre los hechos y diferencias de valores."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.8f9db777-f176-475b-add8-179211562a76.title"
msgid "BetterGov.PH"
msgstr "BetterGov.PH"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.8f9db777-f176-475b-add8-179211562a76.description"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><i>From WeSolve Foundation (Philippines):</i></a> Born from a grassroots anticorruption movement, <a id=\"a2\">this volunteer-run, open-source platform</a> monitors how the government "
"spends money, awards contracts, and manages public projects."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.8f9db777-f176-475b-add8-179211562a76.description"
msgid ""
"Uses a parsing-and-normalization pipeline that turns scattered government records into machine-readable open datasets, then layers automated red-flag analysis over them to surface the projects that "
"journalists and citizens should scrutinize first."
msgstr ""
"Emplea un proceso de análisis y normalización que convierte registros gubernamentales dispersos en conjuntos de datos abiertos legibles por máquinas y, a continuación, aplica sobre ellos un análisis"
" automatizado de señales de alerta para identificar los proyectos que periodistas y ciudadanos deberían examinar con mayor prioridad."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.56b9ae77-e8af-4349-ab40-2e0b21478f28.title"
msgid "Civic Pulse"
msgstr "Civic Pulse"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.56b9ae77-e8af-4349-ab40-2e0b21478f28.description"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><i>From Ciudadanía Inteligente (Chile):</i></a> Piloted in Chile and built to expand across Latin America, this AI-powered early warning system tracks legislative activity and emerging "
"threats to civil society."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.56b9ae77-e8af-4349-ab40-2e0b21478f28.description"
msgid ""
"Ingests legislation and news through public APIs and classifies it with a LlamaIndex retrieval layer over a curated legal corpus, generating risk alerts that human analysts validate before they "
"reach the organizations who act on them."
msgstr ""
"Ingiere legislación y noticias a través de API públicas y las clasifica con una capa de recuperación LlamaIndex sobre un corpus jurídico seleccionado. A partir de ello, genera alertas de riesgo que "
"los analistas humanos validan antes de que lleguen a las organizaciones que actúan en consecuencia."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.0feb51f4-bc34-4fb5-95e2-cf2961731859.title"
msgid "Convoca"
msgstr "Convoca"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.0feb51f4-bc34-4fb5-95e2-cf2961731859.description"
msgid ""
"<i>(United States):</i> Co-designed with city planners in New York City and organizers in North Carolina, <a id=\"a1\">this tool makes sense of large volumes of community input</a>, surfaces "
"recurring themes, and connects public decisions back to what residents actually said."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.0feb51f4-bc34-4fb5-95e2-cf2961731859.description"
msgid "Analyzes everything from sticky notes to recorded dialogue using RAG-grounded sensemaking, providing source-level traceability for every synthesized insight."
msgstr "Analiza desde notas adhesivas hasta diálogos grabados mediante interpretación fundamentada en RAG, lo que proporciona trazabilidad a nivel de fuente para cada conclusión sintetizada."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.97ec1de7-dd8d-44f0-ad47-bf3edd5262a0.title"
msgid "FOIA+"
msgstr "FOIA+"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.97ec1de7-dd8d-44f0-ad47-bf3edd5262a0.description"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><i>From Civio (Spain):</i></a> Grounded in more than a decade of defending the right to information in Spain, this tool helps people navigate the entire freedom-of-information process."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.97ec1de7-dd8d-44f0-ad47-bf3edd5262a0.description"
msgid ""
"Uses RAG to ground responses in Spain's transparency law, regulator resolutions, and court rulings, turning a plain question into a formal request, explaining the government's response, assessing "
"whether a refusal is lawful, and drafting an appeal when it isn't."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza RAG para fundamentar las respuestas en la ley de transparencia española, las resoluciones de los organismos reguladores y la jurisprudencia. Convierte una pregunta sencilla en una solicitud "
"formal, explica la respuesta del gobierno, evalúa si una denegación es conforme a derecho y, cuando no lo es, redacta el correspondiente recurso."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.f6e649e2-31f0-48ea-bc0e-9e0b92205982.title"
msgid "Karakutu"
msgstr "Karakutu"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.f6e649e2-31f0-48ea-bc0e-9e0b92205982.description"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><i>From CORRECTIV (Germany):</i></a> Built for exiled journalists, researchers, and diaspora communities, <a id=\"a2\">this decentralized archive helps make invisible censorship "
"visible</a> by preserving censored journalism in Turkey, where tens of thousands of news articles have disappeared from public view since 2014."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.f6e649e2-31f0-48ea-bc0e-9e0b92205982.description"
msgid "Runs a smart-contract-coordinated miner network that monitors news outlets for deletions, then passes each through a verification pipeline before a human auditor signs off."
msgstr ""
"Ejecuta una red de mineros coordinada por contratos inteligentes que monitoriza los medios de comunicación en busca de eliminaciones y, a continuación, somete cada caso a un proceso de verificación "
"antes de que un auditor humano lo apruebe."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.e2496ab8-a5dc-4027-91b1-7add4ac07c33.title"
msgid "Open Facilitation Library"
msgstr "Open Facilitation Library"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.e2496ab8-a5dc-4027-91b1-7add4ac07c33.description"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><i>From Metagov (United States):</i></a> As AI becomes more involved in public deliberation processes, this project works to define and teach what good facilitation looks like, helping "
"train people and AI systems to support collective decision-making, self-governance, and meaningful public participation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.e2496ab8-a5dc-4027-91b1-7add4ac07c33.description"
msgid "Uses two open-source elicitation agents: one using agentic RAG (<a id=\"a1\">Comhairle</a>), and one that applies embedding-clustering (<a id=\"a2\">Harmonica</a>)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.d214eeb8-0a9c-4800-88bd-7e0331750b17.title"
msgid "PublicAlgo"
msgstr "PublicAlgo"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.d214eeb8-0a9c-4800-88bd-7e0331750b17.description"
msgid ""
"<i>From DICE Network (Czech Republic):</i> Turning transparency obligations into actionable information about how European governments use AI, <a id=\"a1\">this platform transforms public records "
"and freedom-of-information requests</a> into a searchable public record of government AI use."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.d214eeb8-0a9c-4800-88bd-7e0331750b17.description"
msgid "Combines a self-hosted registry, a freedom-of-information request engine, and an LLM document-analysis service to build searchable profiles of each government AI system."
msgstr ""
"Combina un registro autogestionado, un motor de solicitudes de acceso a la información y un servicio de análisis de documentos con LLM para crear perfiles que pueden examinarse de cada sistema de IA"
" gubernamental."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.eb651742-09f8-4a1f-8de0-98c9fa42b34b.title"
msgid "Visual Index"
msgstr "Visual Index"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.eb651742-09f8-4a1f-8de0-98c9fa42b34b.description"
msgid ""
"<i>From Dean Issacharoff (United States):</i> Developed to support the slow, fragmented work of accountability investigations, <a id=\"a1\">this tool helps investigators search thousands of hours of"
" video</a> to uncover evidence of human rights violations and other critical findings in minutes instead of weeks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.eb651742-09f8-4a1f-8de0-98c9fa42b34b.description"
msgid "Builds a multimodal embedding index over large video collections, turning them into searchable databases that can be queried by what is seen or said on screen."
msgstr ""
"Construye un índice de embeddings multimodal sobre grandes colecciones de vídeo, con lo que las convierte en bases de datos consultables en las que puede buscarse según lo que se ve o se dice en "
"pantalla."

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.3cd45f8b-d424-463d-976e-b337bdb4fb41.title"
msgid "Watch Tower"
msgstr "Watch Tower"

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.3cd45f8b-d424-463d-976e-b337bdb4fb41.description"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\"><i>From Amplified Access (Uganda):</i></a> Working across nine local languages in East Africa, <a id=\"a2\">this platform enables communities to report civic incidents</a> through text,"
" voice, and multimedia, helping local organizations identify emerging issues and respond more quickly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.3cd45f8b-d424-463d-976e-b337bdb4fb41.description"
msgid "Reports are processed through a speech-recognition and translation pipeline using fine-tuned, low-resource language models, then classified and plotted onto live maps."
msgstr ""
"Los informes se procesan a través de una canalización de reconocimiento de voz y traducción que utiliza modelos de lenguaje ajustados para idiomas de bajos recursos. Luego, se clasifican y "
"representan en mapas en tiempo real."

msgctxt "body.0a911ab7-c863-49a5-a284-d0de8563120d.title"
msgid "What We’re Learning"
msgstr "Lo que estamos aprendiendo"

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.3b9bc8be-f425-45c0-bb32-e93505f0f28f"
msgid "As we convene with experts and learn alongside our cohort, we’re hearing a lot of the same thing:"
msgstr "A medida que nos reunimos con especialistas y aprendemos junto a nuestra cohorte, escuchamos repetidamente lo mismo:"

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.3b9bc8be-f425-45c0-bb32-e93505f0f28f"
msgid "AI shouldn’t replace people or human decision-making. It should instead help us become more informed, skilled, and engaged in the democratic processes that affect our lives."
msgstr ""
"La IA no debería reemplazar a las personas ni la toma de decisiones humana. En cambio, debería ayudarnos a estar más informados, ser más competentes y participar más activamente en los procesos "
"democráticos que afectan a nuestras vidas."

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.3b9bc8be-f425-45c0-bb32-e93505f0f28f"
msgid ""
"When it comes to AI and democracy, we’re not dealing with an optimization problem. We don’t need AI to automate away the essential messiness and friction of debate, disagreement, and compromise. But"
" that’s the real risk we’re facing: letting democratic life be treated as something to be streamlined, not strengthened."
msgstr ""
"Cuando se trata de IA y democracia, no estamos ante un problema de optimización. No necesitamos que la IA automatice el desorden y la fricción esenciales del debate, el desacuerdo y el compromiso. "
"Pero ese es el verdadero riesgo al que nos enfrentamos: permitir que la vida democrática se trate como algo que hay que agilizar, no fortalecer."

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.3b9bc8be-f425-45c0-bb32-e93505f0f28f"
msgid "We don’t have to take that path. The future of AI is still ours to build."
msgstr "No tenemos que tomar ese camino. Todavía está en nuestras manos construir el futuro de la IA."

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.3b9bc8be-f425-45c0-bb32-e93505f0f28f"
msgid ""
"AI can strengthen democracies when it’s designed to build understanding while keeping the messy but essential process of decision-making in our hands. This can take many forms. It can involve "
"surfacing information that’s fragmented or difficult to access, supporting community discussions, building in transparency, and making participation more visible and connected to the decisions that "
"shape our communities and societies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.3b9bc8be-f425-45c0-bb32-e93505f0f28f"
msgid ""
"Stay tuned as we gather more insights from our cohort, and watch our “AI for Democracy, or Democracy for AI?” panel discussion to hear experts wrestle with some of the biggest questions defining the"
" field today."
msgstr ""
"Permanece al tanto mientras recopilamos más conclusiones de nuestra cohorte, y mira nuestro debate en panel «¿IA para la democracia, o democracia para la IA?» para escuchar a especialistas debatir "
"algunas de las preguntas más importantes que definen el campo hoy en día."

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.left_column.08f0132e-7e50-4e0e-b1a1-02df4e69c7e4.label"
msgid "Watch the panel discussion"
msgstr "Ver el panel de debate"

msgctxt "body.aaa9a0bc-6b2e-4bef-b4c7-cd8c864e59d8.right_column.2caec716-7f63-4fd9-b8b0-ce6f2e5e9924.image.alt_text"
msgid "Democracy isn't meant to be optimized overlayed on sky and shape"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c21b1c60-a308-4f70-ae5e-11beef4ac519.title"
msgid "Why This Work Matters"
msgstr "Por qué este trabajo importa"

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.dcf4710a-e1fb-4c2b-ae89-da3c002b0a3a"
msgid "Technology has always tested and shaped democracy."
msgstr "La tecnología siempre ha puesto a prueba y dado forma a la democracia."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.dcf4710a-e1fb-4c2b-ae89-da3c002b0a3a"
msgid ""
"The printing press broke monopolies on information, fundamentally altering the architecture of power. The telegraph created high-speed networks that erased the barrier of distance, allowing "
"discovery and dissent to travel across continents in an instant. Radio, television, and, eventually, the Internet, brought voices from the margins into the public square."
msgstr ""
"La imprenta destruyó los monopolios sobre la información y alteró fundamentalmente la arquitectura del poder. El telégrafo creó redes de alta velocidad que borraron la barrera de la distancia y "
"permitieron que los descubrimientos y la disidencia viajaran a través de los continentes en un instante. La radio, la televisión y, finalmente, Internet trajeron las voces de los márgenes a la plaza"
" pública."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.e197a179-e9ce-4418-a4ba-154863c74234"
msgid "If history teaches us anything, it's that we can't afford to sit this moment out."
msgstr "Si la historia nos enseña algo, es que no podemos permitirnos no participar en este momento decisivo."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.e197a179-e9ce-4418-a4ba-154863c74234"
msgid ""
"Democratic progress is never a permanent win. It ebbs and flows: power recalibrates, adapting to new tools of influence. Today we’re called to experiment, to create new spaces for imagination, test "
"new ideas, and learn from one another."
msgstr ""
"El progreso democrático nunca es un logro permanente. Avanza y retrocede: el poder se recalibra, adaptándose a las nuevas herramientas de influencia. Hoy se nos llama a experimentar, crear nuevos "
"espacios para la imaginación, probar nuevas ideas y aprender los unos de los otros."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.a47a9390-c81b-4ff1-a9b9-c7068303b742"
msgid "Because AI is already reshaping democratic life."
msgstr "Porque la IA ya está reconfigurando la vida democrática."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.a47a9390-c81b-4ff1-a9b9-c7068303b742"
msgid ""
"We’re only just beginning to see how it’s reconfiguring systems and structures of power, yet the consequences are unfolding in real time. The coalitions that sustain democratic life are becoming "
"harder to hold together, placing even more pressure on democratic societies around the world. As power concentrates, we risk losing agency over the technologies that govern our lives and shape how "
"we understand the world, and each other. And no single community or country has all the answers. Progress depends on learning across borders and building on one another's experiments."
msgstr ""
"Apenas estamos empezando a ver cómo está reconfigurando los sistemas y las estructuras de poder, pero las consecuencias se están desarrollando en tiempo real. Las coaliciones que sostienen la vida "
"democrática son cada vez más difíciles de mantener unidas, lo que ejerce aún más presión sobre las sociedades democráticas de todo el mundo. A medida que el poder se concentra, corremos el riesgo de"
" perder el control sobre las tecnologías que gobiernan nuestras vidas y dan forma a cómo entendemos el mundo y a los demás. Y ninguna comunidad ni país tiene todas las respuestas. El progreso "
"depende de aprender a través de las fronteras y de desarrollar los experimentos de los demás."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.40382ec6-c196-47fc-9d03-a47284c74572"
msgid "The future of AI and democracy hasn’t been written yet."
msgstr "El futuro de la IA y la democracia aún no está escrito."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.40382ec6-c196-47fc-9d03-a47284c74572"
msgid ""
"It’s still ours to build. People around the world are already rejecting the status quo, adding to a growing counter-movement that turns imagination into infrastructure for experimentation, "
"reinvention, and renewal. By choosing openness over secrecy and public benefit over narrow profit, we can create technologies that give power back to people and their communities."
msgstr ""
"Todavía está en nuestras manos construirlo. Personas de todo el mundo ya están rechazando el statu quo, sumándose a un contramovimiento creciente que convierte la imaginación en infraestructura para"
" la experimentación, la reinvención y la renovación. Al elegir la apertura frente al secretismo y el beneficio público frente al lucro privado, podemos crear tecnologías que devuelvan el poder a las"
" personas y a sus comunidades."

msgctxt "body.ca09521f-22ed-47b6-979d-683419d5f7b2.left_column.3ed18f63-3d38-4bf4-bcb9-7b987032e682"
msgid ""
"Our Democracy x AI cohort is rooted in the belief that AI can still strengthen democratic life, but only if alternative technologies and ideas are supported early enough to survive, scale, and take "
"root. By investing in people and projects that are building in the public interest, Mozilla Foundation is planting the seeds for a more open, democratic future with AI."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra cohorte Democracy x AI se asienta en la convicción de que la IA todavía puede fortalecer la vida democrática, pero solo si las tecnologías e ideas alternativas reciben apoyo con suficiente "
"antelación para sobrevivir, escalar y arraigar. Al invertir en personas y proyectos que construyen en beneficio del interés público, la Fundación Mozilla está sembrando las semillas de un futuro más"
" abierto y democrático con la IA."

